<p><%= link_to "Make a bid", candidates_path %> and help a great cause. But there is more to Cut the Chi than making a bid: Be sure to attend the event September 18 and take some time to learn about who your bid will support. Any questions? <a href="mailto:j_gualco@u.pacific.edu">Contact Us.</a></p>
